<body>
<div><head>袁崧宜都山川記</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-1a.2">江水東過秭歸縣南。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-1a.3">屈原有賢秭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-1a.4">閒原放逐，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-1a.5">亦來歸喻令自寬。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-1a.6">全鄉人冀其見從，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-1a.7">因名曰秭歸，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-1a.8">即《離騷》所謂女嬃嬋媛以詈余也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-1a.9">《水經注》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-1a.10">秭歸蓋楚子熊繹之始國，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-1a.11">而屈原之鄉里也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-1a.12">屈原宅於今具存。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-2a.2">父老傳言原既流放，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-2a.3">忽然暫歸，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-2a.4">鄉人喜悅，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-2a.5">因名曰歸鄉。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-2a.6">抑其山秀水清，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-2a.7">故出儁異，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-2a.8">地嶮流疾，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-2a.9">故具性亦隘。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-2a.10">詩云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-2a.11">惟嶽降神，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-2a.12">生甫及申。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-2a.13">信與！<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-2a.14">並同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-3a.2">峽中猿鳴至清，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-3a.3">諸山谷傳其響，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-3a.4">泠泠不絕。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-3a.5">行者歌之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-3a.6">巴東三峽猿鳴悲，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-3a.7">猿鳴三聲淚沾衣。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-3a.8">《類聚》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-3a.9">宜都山絕崖壁立數百丈，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-3a.10">有一火燼插其崖間，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-3a.11">望可長數尺。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-3a.12">傳云堯洪水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-3a.13">人泊船此旁爨餘，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-3a.14">故曰插竈。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-3a.15">《御覽》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-4a.2">自蜀至流頭灘五千餘里，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-4a.3">下水五日，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-4a.4">上水百日也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-4a.5">渡流頭灘十里便得宜昌縣。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-4a.6">東逕狼尾灘而歷人灘，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-4a.7">二灘相去二里。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-4a.8">人灘水至峻陗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-4a.9">南岸有青石，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-4a.10">夏沒冬出，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-4a.11">其石嶔崟，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-4a.12">數十步中，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-4a.13">悉作人面形，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-4a.14">或大或小，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-4a.15">其分明者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-4a.16">鬚髮皆具，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-4a.17">因名曰人灘也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-4a.18">並《水經注》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-5a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-5a" ed="CHANT" n="001-5a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-5a.2">自峽口沂江百許里至黃牛灘，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-5a.3">南岸有重山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-5a.4">山嶺有石壁，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-5a.5">上有人負刀牽黃牛，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-5a.6">人跡所絕，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-5a.7">莫得究焉。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-5a.8">《類聚》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-5a.9">自黃牛灘東入西陵界至峽口一百許里，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-5a.10">山水紆曲，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-5a.11">而兩岸高山重嶂，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-5a.12">非日中夜半，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-5a.13">不見日月。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-5a.14">絕壁或千許丈，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-5a.15">其石彩色，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-5a.16">形容多所象類。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-5a.17">林木高茂，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-5a.18">略盡冬春。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-5a.19">猿鳴至清，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-5a.20">山谷傳響，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-5a.21">泠泠不絕，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-5a.22">所謂三峽，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-5a.23">此其一也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-5a.24">《水經注》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-6a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-6a" ed="CHANT" n="001-6a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-6a.2">自西陵北行十三里，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-6a.3">有石穴名馬穴，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-6a.4">嘗有白馬出食，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-6a.5">人逐之入穴，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-6a.6">潛出漢中，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-6a.7">人失馬亦嘗出穴，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-6a.8">相去數里。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-6a.9">《御覽》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-6a.10">自西陵東北陸行百二十里，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-6a.11">有方山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-6a.12">其嶺四方，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-6a.13">素崖如壁，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-6a.14">天晴朗時，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-6a.15">有黃影似人像。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-6a.16">山上有神祠場特生一竹，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-6a.17">茂好，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-6a.18">其標垂場中，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-6a.19">場中有塵埃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-6a.20">則風起動此竹，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-6a.21">拂去如灑掃者。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-6a.22">《類聚》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-7a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-7a" ed="CHANT" n="001-7a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-7a.2">對西陵江南岸有山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-7a.3">其峰孤秀，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-7a.4">自山南至嶺，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-7a.5">俯臨大江如縈帶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-7a.6">視舟船如鳧鴈。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-7a.7">《初學記》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-7a.8">江北多連山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-7a.9">登之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-7a.10">望江南諸山數十百重，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-7a.11">莫識其名。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-7a.12">高者千仞，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-7a.13">多奇形異勢，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-7a.14">自非烟褰雨霽，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-7a.15">不辨見此奇山矣。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-7a.16">《水經注》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-8a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-8a" ed="CHANT" n="001-8a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-8a.2">郡城即陸抗攻步闡拒晉於此壘。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-8a.3">《寰宇記》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-8a.4">大江清濁分流，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-8a.5">其水十丈見底，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-8a.6">視魚遊如乘空，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-8a.7">淺處多五色石。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-8a.8">南崖有山名荊門，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-8a.9">北崖有山名虎牙，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-8a.10">二山相對。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-8a.11">其荊門山在南，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-8a.12">上合而下空徹，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-8a.13">山南有像門也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-8a.14">並《御覽》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-9a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-9a" ed="CHANT" n="001-9a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-9a.2">虎牙山有石壁，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-9a.3">其色黃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-9a.4">間有白文，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-9a.5">亦有牙齒形。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-9a.6">《寰宇記》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-9a.7">郡西北三十里有丹山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-9a.8">天晴，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-9a.9">山嶺忽有霧起，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-9a.10">迴轉如烟，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-9a.11">不過再朝，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-9a.12">雨必降。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-9a.13">《御覽》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-10a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-10a" ed="CHANT" n="001-10a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-10a.2">佷山縣東有溫泉注大溪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-10a.3">夏纔暖，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-10a.4">冬則大熱，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-10a.5">上常有霧氣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-10a.6">百病久疾，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-10a.7">入此水多愈。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-10a.8">《初學記》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-10a.9">佷山縣東六十里有山名下魚城，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-10a.10">四面絕崖，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-10a.11">唯雨道可上，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-10a.12">皆嶮峻。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-10a.13">山上周迴可二十里，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-10a.14">有林木池水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-10a.15">民田種於山上。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-10a.16">昔永嘉亂，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-10a.17">土人登此避賊，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-10a.18">賊守之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-10a.19">經年食盡，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-10a.20">取池魚擲下與賊，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-10a.21">以示不窮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-10a.22">賊遂退散，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-10a.23">因此名為下魚城。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-10a.24">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-11a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-11a" ed="CHANT" n="001-11a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-11a.2">佷山山谷之內有石穴，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-11a.3">穴出清泉，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-11a.4">下有神魚，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-11a.5">大者二尺，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-11a.6">小者一尺，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-11a.7">釣者先請多少，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-11a.8">拜而請之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-11a.9">數滿便止。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-11a.10">水側有異花，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-11a.11">欲摘之者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-11a.12">亦如魚請。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-11a.13">又有異木，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-11a.14">名千歲木，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-11a.15">葉似棗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-11a.16">冬夏青，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-11a.17">青復有蒼，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-11a.18">范溪相近。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-11a.19">《御覽》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-12a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-12a" ed="CHANT" n="001-12a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-12a.2">佷山縣方室有靈祠，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-12a.3">祠中有特生一竹，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-12a.4">壇美高危，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-12a.5">其杪下垂，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-12a.6">忽有塵穢，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-12a.7">起風動竹，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-12a.8">拂蕩如掃。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-12a.9">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-12a.10">佷山縣北有石穴，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-12a.11">平居無水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-12a.12">有渴者至，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-12a.13">誠請乞，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-12a.14">輒得。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-12a.15">戲乞則不得。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-12a.16">《書鈔》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-13a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-13a" ed="CHANT" n="001-13a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-13a.2">佷山縣南岸有谿，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-13a.3">名長陽，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-13a.4">此谿數異上重山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-13a.5">岡嶺廻曲，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-13a.6">有射堂村，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-13a.7">東六七里有石穴，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-13a.8">清泉流三十步，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-13a.9">便入穴中，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-13a.10">即當陽谿源也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-14a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-14a" ed="CHANT" n="001-14a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-14a.2">亭下村有石穴，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-14a.3">甚深，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-14a.4">未曾測其遠近。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-14a.5">穴中有蝙蝠，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-14a.6">大如鳥，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-14a.7">多倒懸。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-14a.8">並同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-14a.9">亭下村有淵，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-14a.10">淵有神龍，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-14a.11">每旱，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-14a.12">百姓輒以𦱌草投淵上，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-14a.13">流魚死，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-14a.14">龍怒，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-14a.15">應時大雨。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-14a.16">《御覽》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-15a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-15a" ed="CHANT" n="001-15a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-15a.2">夷水又東逕石室，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-15a.3">作層巖之上，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-15a.4">石室南向，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-15a.5">水出其下，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-15a.6">縣崖千仞，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-15a.7">自水上逕望見每有陟山嶺者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-15a.8">扳木側足而行，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-15a.9">莫知其誰。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-15a.10">邨人駱都，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-15a.11">小時到此室邊採蜜，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-15a.12">見一仙人坐石床上，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-15a.13">見都，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-15a.14">凝矚不轉。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-15a.15">都還招鄉人同往，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-15a.16">則不復見。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-15a.17">鄉人今名為仙人室。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-15a.18">都孫昔尚存。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-15a.19">《水經注》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-16a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-16a" ed="CHANT" n="001-16a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-16a.2">自鹽水西北行五十餘里，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-16a.3">有一山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-16a.4">獨立峻絕，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-16a.5">名為難留城。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-16a.6">從西面上里餘得石穴，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-16a.7">行百許步，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-16a.8">得石磧，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-16a.9">有二文石，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-16a.10">並在穴中。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-16a.11">《書鈔》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-17a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-17a" ed="CHANT" n="001-17a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-17a.2">宜陽山有風井穴，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-17a.3">大如甕，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-17a.4">夏出冬入。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-17a.5">有樵人置笠穴口，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-17a.6">風吸之入，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-17a.7">後於長陽溪口得笠，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-17a.8">則知潛通焉。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-17a.9">《御覽》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-17a.10">登句將山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-17a.11">見馬鬣建鼓，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-17a.12">嶷然半天。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-18a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-18a" ed="CHANT" n="001-18a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-18a.2">登句將北，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-18a.3">見高斧山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-18a.4">嶷然半天。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-18a.5">並《寰宇記》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-18a.6">登句將山南，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-18a.7">望見宜都江陵，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-18a.8">近在目前，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-18a.9">沮潭&amp;CH-0F0261;漢，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-18a.10">諸山嵎嵎。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-18a.11">時見。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-18a.12">遠眺雲夢之渾，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-18a.13">晶然與天際，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-18a.14">回顧總視眾山數千仞者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-18a.15">森然羅列於足下，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-18a.16">千仞以還者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-18a.17">𡾋嵬如邱浪勢焉，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-18a.18">今在上洛縣西北。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-18a.19">《御覽》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-19a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-19a" ed="CHANT" n="001-19a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-19a.2">縣去山四十里別從狼尾灘下南崖。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1733_CHANT_001-19a.3">《初學記》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
